                           <ab type="conservation">Darkened brown papyrus with coarse surface; badly damaged at the left to top and top; broken off at the right side; part of the left margin can be seen at the bottom; there is a dark blot of dirt at the upper part; there are some holes and lacunae at several parts. The preserved text is legible; there is a small piece of fiber is folded on to verso.</ab>
